$$
\frac{4(3k) + 5(2k)}{4(3k) - 5(2k)}
=
\frac{12k + 10k}{12k - 10k}
=
\frac{22k}{2k}
=
\frac{11}{1}
$$

So the ratio is $11 : 1$.

